    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043080/extras/91c29b89d78c30c2de45be36adf1ce5f.poster.avif?t=1740387083\" width=700 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043080/extras/91c29b89d78c30c2de45be36adf1ce5f.webm?t=1740387083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043080/extras/91c29b89d78c30c2de45be36adf1ce5f.mp4?t=1740387083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Healthy Food Corporation is a food giant, which complete construction of mega factories network. After a successful launch, Healthy Food will become a total monopoly of the food market on Earth. You will have to fight against fast-food monsters brought to life by the Healthy Food Corporation to protect their evil plans! <br><br>The design of the main characters is based on a Matryoshka doll. During the game, the player will be able to change the main character by simply switching between Matryoshka dolls inside. Each hero has a unique set of skills, and by selecting the right hero during battle, you can significantly change the outcome of the fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043080/extras/c9da88af30238098652213afa4a3451b.poster.avif?t=1740387083\" width=700 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043080/extras/c9da88af30238098652213afa4a3451b.webm?t=1740387083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043080/extras/c9da88af30238098652213afa4a3451b.mp4?t=1740387083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight and explore a colorful, 3D isometric claymation-style world to stop the corporation's evil plans and uncover the terrible secret behind the living fast-food monsters!</p>",
